Blocks.Text: Payment Methods Accepted: Cash, Credit Card, Debit Card, Insurance Billing
Thank you for choosing Medical Center Hospital.
We wish you a speedy recovery.
1. Payment is due within 30 days of discharge date.
2. Late payments will incur a 1.5% monthly interest charge.
3. Please reference your Patient ID and Bill Number when making payments.
4. Insurance claims will be processed within 14 business days.
